    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CqlQueryRenderIterator

    public class CqlQueryFilterIterator
extends org.apache.accumulo.core.iterators.user.WholeRowIterator
    This class extends from the WholeRowIterator (encapsulating an entire row of key/value pairs into a single key/value pair) but also provides CQL filtering on the tablet servers. It requires a FeatureDataAdapter to interpret whole rows as SimpleFeatures and it will decode a CQL filter string into a query filter to check acceptance with each SimpleFeature within an AccumuloIterator and skip the row if it is not accepted.
